tic80 (1.1.2837-1) trixie; urgency=low

  * Package TIC-80 v1.1.2837 for armhf from source against the system SDL2 +
    mesa GLES2/EGL via SDLGPU, for the CHIP's Mali400/lima GPU. Upstream's
    rpi.deb links the Broadcom GLES blobs and does not run on the CHIP.
  * Replaces the proprietary PICO-8 in pocket-home's "Play" button; TIC-80's
    240x136 framebuffer is an exact 2x of the 480x272 PocketCHIP panel.

